2002-1927 (La. 10/25/02)

Dorothy POULLARD v. DIOCESE OF LAFAYETTE. No. 2002-C-1927. Supreme Court of Louisiana. Oct. 25, 2002.

In re Poullard, Dorothy; — Plaintiff; Applying for Writ of Certiorari and/or Review Office Of Workers’ Compensation District 02, No. 00-08569; to the Court of Appeal, Third Circuit, No. 02-110.

Denied.

JOHNSON, J., would grant the writ.
